textAnnotations.description:
IDON'T BELIEVE ITS NECESSARY
TO PAY MILLIONS IN BRIBES
TO BEHEARD IN WASHINGTON
I BELIEVE NECESSARY
TO SPEAK CLEARLY
INTO THE LAMP.
